		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You separate your swarm body, allowing you to avoid part of an attack or effect meant to hurt you.</em></p><p><strong>Reaction</strong> - Self - 1 Round - 3/Long Rest - Magical</p><p><em>Trigger: While @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.W6yKtk7Svvy9dIq9]{raging}, you take acid, cold, fire, force, electric, necrotic, radiant, or sonic damage from an attack or ability that isn't an area of effect.</em></p><ul><li><p>You gain resistance to the above damage types, except from area of effect abilities, including the triggering damage.</p></li></ul>",
